OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780675876
OL,3,CPolice find haul of zombie knives and
OL,4,Crubber mask in car
OL,6,FPolice made an "alarming discovery"
OL,7,Fafter stopping a car on the motorway
OL,8,Fand uncovering a haul of more than 40
OL,9,Fdangerous weapons - and a rubber face
OL,10,Fmask.
OL,12,FOfficers conducting a routine patrol
OL,13,Fon the M6 in Cheshire pulled over a
OL,14,Fred Volkswagen Polo at around 11.40pm
OL,15,Fon Thursday, 28 May.
OL,17,FThe vehicle was stopped near Junction
OL,18,F17 after Automatic Number Plate
OL,19,FRecognition (ANPR) enquiries revealed
OL,20,Fit was linked to weapons offences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
