FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780675876
OL,3,CPolice find haul of zombie knives and
OL,4,Crubber mask in car
OL,6,FInside the car, police found two
OL,7,Foccupants from the Birmingham area - a
OL,8,Fman, 19, and an 18-year-old woman - as
OL,9,Fwell as several boxes packed with
OL,10,F"dangerous" weapons.
OL,12,FCheshire Police seized more than 40
OL,13,Fblades, including zombie-style knives,
OL,14,Fmachetes and knuckledusters - as well
OL,15,Fas a rubber face mask.
OL,17,FBoth occupants were arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of possession of a bladed
OL,19,Farticle in a public place and
OL,20,Fpossessing offensive weapons for the
OL,21,Fpurpose of sale.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780675876
OL,3,CPolice find haul of zombie knives and
OL,4,Crubber mask in car
OL,6,FCheshire Constabulary has since
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the 19-year-old man has
OL,8,Fbeen "eliminated from the
OL,9,Finvestigation", while the 18-year-old
OL,10,Fwoman has been released on conditional
OL,11,Fbail.
OL,13,FChief Inspector Joe McNally praised
OL,14,Fthe instincts of the officers on the
OL,15,Fground.
OL,17,F"I'd like to thank the quick-thinking
OL,18,Fofficers who were on patrol in the
OL,19,Farea at the time and acted on instinct
OL,20,Fto pull over the vehicle, leading to
OL,21,Fthis alarming discovery," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
