PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780675876
OL,3,CPolice find haul of zombie knives and
OL,4,Crubber mask in car
OL,6,F"These blades will soon be destroyed,
OL,7,Fpermanently preventing possibility of
OL,8,Fthem being used on our streets and
OL,9,Ffalling into the wrong hands."
